{"tid":2325279,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警察福利基金總收入較上年增逾8倍","createTime":"2020-12-14T12:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T12:52:59.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7f02ac7678861f1ab41abee5f62db6dc3b1f152f","tid":2325279,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:40:04.000Z","msg":"警察福利基金19至20年度總收入近1.9億元，比上個年度不足2000萬元相比，增加超過8倍，盈餘近7400萬元。截至今年3月底，基金資產淨產為近2.6億元，較對上一年度淨增幅約40%。<br />\n<br />\n警察福利基金向立法會提交文件，顯示捐款收入增加1.7億元，升幅高達26倍，但「僱用警察服務費用」、「定期存款利息」和「承辦商代售紀念品佣金」的收入都減少。<br />\n<br />\n至於支出方面，「擔任特殊職務警務人員茶點費用」增加近6400萬，增幅約52倍，「發給陷入困難的警務和文職人員補助金」，亦增加320多萬，增幅亦超過50%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565253-20201214.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565253-20201214.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4UWfeJE2Id0Ic3Ynx8r7n4lS5wRbVpD6X1tjwtO29R8%3D&h=e1839bbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565253-20201214.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4b060949\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565253-20201214.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"156b45b49bddb0ca072037d41681e50d0e1b632c","tid":2325279,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:41:26.000Z","msg":"藍絲保護廢"},{"pid":"74e25247c6c8aab0f48563bcf49a087d7c10b2b4","tid":2325279,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:46:51.000Z","msg":"資金流向好可疑！"},{"pid":"5908812c660e4bc2478dde263c1c91d0f73336f7","tid":2325279,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:48:16.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>洗黑錢</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n光明正大用捐款收陀地<br />\n過街老鼠死賤種"},{"pid":"4e45ade6c362232df351be6155584f16ec98f943","tid":2325279,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202